  "description": "A nighttime aerial view of a cityscape with a prominent bridge and a vibrant fireworks display. The bridge, illuminated with white lights, stretches across a dark body of water. Behind the bridge, a city skyline rises, featuring numerous buildings lit with a warm, golden glow. Above the skyline, a burst of colorful fireworks explodes, creating a spectacular show of light. The fireworks are a mix of red, white, and gold, contrasting with the darker hues of the night sky and the surrounding landscape. The overall scene evokes a sense of celebration and grandeur.",
